So go on, then.

7
00:20:37.527 --> 00:20:38.737 
威胁。
Menace.

8
00:20:38.820 --> 00:20:40.656 
好吧，好吧。啊哼。
Alright, alright. Ahem.

9
00:20:42.407 --> 00:20:44.910 
你觉得这够邪恶吗，林德太太？隐马尔可夫模型？
Is this evil enough for you, Mrs. Lynde? Hmm?

10
