-嗯？你怎么认为？隐马尔可夫模型？-[林德太太大笑]
-Hmm? What do you think? Hmm? -[Mrs. Lynde laughing]

11
00:20:48.538 --> 00:20:50.123 
[嘘嘘，大笑]
[shushing, laughing]

12
00:20:50.207 --> 00:20:52.960 
-[笑声]-你真有才华，科尔。
-[laughter] -You're so talented, Cole.

